sources.description:
Best friends since college, two young women mount their first art show in a small New England town. Though Sarah is engaged and Amy feigns disinterest, both are subconsciously searching for the perfect man. When enigmatic strangers enter Sarah and Amy’s cautious lives, a mystery involving drugs, the CIA and Sarah’s beloved uncle unfolds while romance blossoms.
